</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Tokyo" /><category term="Views" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking over the Minato Mirai area of Yokohama, on a clear day from the Landmark Tower. The tall buildings in the distance are the Tokyo skyline.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2308_A7R00368.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2023/2308_A7R00368.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Shinjuku Evening・夜の新宿</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230824/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Shinjuku Evening・夜の新宿" /><published>2023-08-24T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2023-08-24T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/tocho</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/230824/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
